channel.title: Need Someone to run a server
channel.description:
I have a mac. I can't find anyplace to help me run my server. :( so i would like to know if someone would want to.
I just need to know when it will be up and not up.
My Website is pwn.smfforfree3.com
The server should be named pwn, something. I don't have ip's, just the source. If anyone is interested, you will be a admin and a admin/Server runner on our site. If someone does, we can talk about it more somewhere else. I will spend lots of time developing the server. I just can't run it :/
Thanks, hope your interested.
-Shane
